data.description: Welcome to Rosena Ranch, where comfort meets resort style living in a community you'll adore. This home has a spacious design and is a true gem for those seeking comfort, style, and a touch of elegance. Step into the inviting living room with large sunlit windows that draw you to a view of the spacious backyard. Natural light shines in the room, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and gatherings. The focal point of the living room is a cozy fireplace, adorned with a sophisticated Carrera marble surround. It not only adds an element of warmth but also serves as a stunning centerpiece that exudes elegance and charm. Surrounding the fireplace is a custom-built entertainment center that enhances both functionality and aesthetics that provides a stylish home for your decor or entertainment equipment, merging beauty and function. The living room flows into the kitchen and dining area, creating an open-concept space that's perfect for entertaining guests. Whether it's an intimate family meal or a gathering with friends, this layout ensures everyone feels connected and comfortable. Step outside to a generously sized backyard-larger than most in the community, ideal for children's play, outdoor dining, or enjoying the fresh air. Rosena Ranch offers not just a home, but a lifestyle. The recreation center offers your family a Jr. Olympic lap pool, splash park, clubhouse and fitness center. The recreation center includes a beach entry pool, spa, picnic area with barbecues and more! It is the perfect place for your family to spend time relaxing and soaking up the sun, hold meetings, birthday parties, or any other type of get together.
